<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Love of Learning</title>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.0.0-alpha1/jquery.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/underscore.js/1.8.3/underscore-min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/backbone.js/1.2.2/backbone-min.js"></script>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald|Raleway|Lato' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.5.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/learning.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">

</head>
<body>

	<header>
		<header>
    <data id="username" style="display: none;"><%= username %></data>
    <ul id="header-links">
      <li><a href="/index">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/users/<%= username %>/">Dashboard</a></li>
      <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
      <ul>
        <li id="form-li">
          <form action="/users/<%= username %>/past" method="POST">
            <select name="values" id="dropdown" value="Past Entries">
              <option selected disabled>View Past Entries</option>
              <option value="learning">Love of Learning</option>
              <option value="humility">Humility</option>
              <option value="openness">Openness</option>
              <option value="tolerance">Tolerance</option>
              <option value="generosity">Generosity</option>
              <option value="autonomy">Autonomy</option>
              <option value="honesty">Honesty</option>
            </select>
            <button type="submit"><i class="fa fa-history fa-1x"></i></button>
          </form>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
	</header>

	<section>
		<h1>Love of Learning</h1>
		<article>Most of us are born with some degree of curiousity about the world around us, but this quality can also be cultivated simply by investigating areas and ideas that are outside of our regular sphere or "comfort zone."</article>
	</section>
	<hr>
	<form id="question-form" action="/users/<%= username %>/learning/create" method="post">

		<input type="hidden" name="username" value="<%= username %>">

		<div class="question">
			<h3 id="question-1">Name an idea or skill that I've added to my arsenal, or am working on adding.
			</h3>
			<textarea form="question-form" id="question-1-textarea" name="answer1" cols="80" rows="10" placeholder="Example: learning a language, working on my swimming stroke, learning to program"></textarea>
			<input type="hidden" name="question1" value="Name an idea or skill that I've added to my arsenal, or am working on adding.">
				<div class="past-answers">
					<h4>Previous Entries</h4>
						<% rows.forEach(function (row) { %>
						<% if (row.answer1 === '') { %>
								<p>nothin</p>
						<% } else { %>
								<p><%= row.timestamp %>: <%= row.answer1 %></p>
						<% } %>
					<% }) %>
				</div>
		</div>

		<div class="question">
			<h3 id="question-2">What was the best book or article I read recently, and what was the main thing I learned from it?
			</h3>
			<textarea form="question-form" id="question-2-textarea" name="answer2" cols="80" rows="10" placeholder="What have you learned from a recent book or article?"></textarea>
			<input type="hidden" name="question2" value="What was the best book or article I read recently, and what was the main thing I learned from it?">
			<div class="past-answers">
				<h4>Previous Entries</h4>
					<% rows.forEach(function (row) { %>
						<% if (row.answer2 === '') { %>
								<p></p>
						<% } else { %>
								<p><%= row.timestamp %>: <%= row.answer2 %></p>
						<% } %>
					<% }) %>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="question">
			<h3 id="question-3">What was the best movie I saw recently, and what was the main thing I got out of it?
			</h3>
			<textarea form="question-form" id="question-3-textarea" name="answer3" cols="80" rows="10" placeholder="Seen anything good lately? What did you learn?"></textarea>
			<input type="hidden" name="question3" value="What was the best movie I saw recently, and what was the main thing I got out of it?">
			<div class="past-answers">
				<h4>Previous Entries</h4>
				<% rows.forEach(function (row) { %>
						<% if (row.answer3 === '') { %>
								<p></p>
						<% } else { %>
								<p><%= row.timestamp %>: <%= row.answer3 %></p>
						<% } %>
					<% }) %>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="question">
			<h3>Do you have an additional thought about the topic that was not addressed by one of the prompts?</h3>
			<textarea name="random_thought" id="random-textarea" cols="80" rows="10" placeholder="The perfect place for a random thought!"></textarea>
		<div class="past-answers" id="random-answer">
			<h4>Previous Entries</h4>
			<% rows.forEach(function (row) { %>
				<% if (!row.random) { %>
					<% console.log('nothing'); %>
					<% } else { %>
				<p><%= row.timestamp %>: <%= row.random %></p>
				<% } %>
			<% }) %>
		</div>
		</div>
		<br>
		<input id="learning-submit-button" type="submit" value="Submit Answers">

	</form>

	<script src="/javascript/learning.js"></script>
</body>
</html>